						               													<description>From the designer: &amp;quot;You&amp;rsquo;re lucky. See a &amp;ldquo;bug&amp;rdquo; on the ground you just &amp;ldquo;squish&amp;rdquo; 'em with your foot. No problem, right? Well in the far future on planets far away it isn&amp;rsquo;t so easy anymore.&amp;rsquo;Cause the &amp;ldquo;bugs&amp;rdquo; are bigger than you and have appetites to match. You&amp;rsquo;ve seen them. Aliens&amp;hellip;Starship Troopers*&amp;hellip; know what I&amp;rsquo;m saying? That&amp;rsquo;s what this is all about. This&amp;hellip;&amp;rdquo;Bugs!&amp;rdquo; It&amp;rsquo;s about us against them. So what are you waiting for? Not afraid of a little bug, are you?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;BUGS -It&amp;rsquo;s an easy to play miniatures game where the bugs are big with an attitude and it&amp;rsquo;s your job to turn them into &amp;ldquo;pink mist&amp;rdquo; before they &amp;ldquo;slice and dice&amp;rdquo; you. Man against bug at the personal level. Each figure represents either a human or a &amp;ldquo;bug&amp;rdquo;. &amp;#10;This fast and furious game is playable in an hour or two and great for a change of pace or as a day to day thing. Whether you play with a friend or play solo, &amp;ldquo;BUGS&amp;rdquo; will provide hours of enjoyment at very little cost.&amp;#10;Hmmm, fun and cheap. That&amp;rsquo;s something the hobby could use more of....&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Simple skirmish combat between humans and bugs.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
